<p>You know how it is; suddenly you get this great idea, and it's a mad dash to the keyboard to jot it all down. Then you sit on it for months and months untill you go back and make it look presentable.</p>
<p>Note that I did send this around on the forums for comments… several months ago. I don't think anyone said anything more descriptive than "Keep it up, d00d.".</p>
<p>So how is it? Any feedback is appreciated.</p>

